<A>__{all we see are three faces on the screen mouthing words but we can imagine a terrible struggle taking place before us: a man with scissors lunging at his wife, her anguished scream, the whimpering cries of their son. and then there is silence, and it is over, and the three faces instantly return to their impassive porcelain state. their eyes slowly close. they do not move. so that when they do move again, it is startling. in abrupt unison, the eyes flash open. three pairs of eyes stare straight at us, accusing. three mouths open, but speak, in rasping tones, as one.}
